[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/snatch">Snatch</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/snatch">Snatch</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user steals the effects of any healing or status-changing move the foe attempts to use.</p>